Dieses Tutorium soll als Einführung in [[Image:Part_EditAttachment.svg|24px]][[Part_EditAttachment/de|Part Befestigen]] dienen. Es ist nicht umfangreich, wird aber hoffentlich Anwendern beim Ausprobieren helfen.

Attachment is a utility to attach an object to another one. This links the two objects' placement properties, the attached object will then follow the original(if its placement is changed.) The focus is on Part Design workbench and  attaching sketches to other sketches, this being a recommended method for making [[Feature_editing#Advice_for_creating_stable_models|''stable'']] models.<br/>
This tutorial was written for V0.19, but should be valid for any version 0.17 and later. However, things may differ in some details.<br/>
The original model was designed by Md. Aminul Islam and downloaded from here:-https://grabcad.com/library/50-cad-exercise-drawing-1 as "Practice - 13".


